jobs/industries would just stiff you with the bill, where worker compensation is already figured in.<br><br>For some reason tipped is the one that gets the largest amount of press, why?  Because you directly control how much the person earns?<br>And tipped usually makes the least amount of difference in a patrons wallet?  A dollar for that cup of coffee? 15% on that  $60 dinner?  Pennies compared to the 20% commission that salesman just made when you rolled off the lot in your shiney SUV.<br><br>What's the difference? Simple, you didn't see the 20% written anywhere.  Yet, you do see the dollar laying on the table being snapped up by the waitress.<br><br>Ceru<br> <p><center> <a href="http://www.magelo.com/eq_view_profile.html?num=10051"> <img src="http://www.perfectblueproductions.com/eric/cerunew2.jpg" border="0"></a></center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#666666><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub4.ezboard.com/utoxxthewizard.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Toxx The Wizard</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Veteran</span><br>  Posts: 413<br> <font color=#E9D756>(5/30/02 5:33:17 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub4.ezboard.com/femarrdragonsandplanes.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=3371.topic&index=9>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Because some people just don't understand English</span><hr size=1> I am probably trashing any donations I may get by saying this, but if you don't donate, I still do TL. There will be a brief, 30 second pause. . .(Some people carry too much money. . )<br><br>Whether it's a 120k horse or not, I was just making a point. <!--EZCODE EMOTICON START 8) --><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/intl/aenglish/images/emoticons/glasses.gif ALT="8)"><!--EZCODE EMOTICON END-->  <p><center> -- I'm a wizard, naturally I can solo/tank anything. Grouping and guilding is merely a social thing--<br>Toxx Wyrmbane 53 wiz, Heart of Fenris </cen